{"tid":1204343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"若是人生，錯過這一晚，怕再沒機會任意呼喊","createTime":"2019-06-11T14:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T14:56:28.000Z","uid":907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"648e4d1fcb44a8c76f36d74d86f29cd0ba1ce819","tid":1204343,"uid":907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:54:09.000Z","msg":"修定送中逃犯條例，再唔係&rdquo;返工不了&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n香港呢個屋企，人人都有責任守護。<br />\n<br />\n如果今次通過修例，莫須有隨時係香港發生。<br />\n<br />\n面對暴政，一定要以暴易暴。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔可以承擔衝擊前線所引起嘅後果同責任，我都希望你可以企岀黎，提供物資又好，到場聲援都好。你地每一個都咁重要，一致槍口對外。<br />\n<br />\n約定你今晚野餐！<br />\n<br />\n最後機會！再唔岀聲，再唔岀黎！以後都無機會！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OGJhQMv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGJhQMv.png&h=dc87d1ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C_23GElzJFo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC_23GElzJFo&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TifsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=d411a30f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C_23GElzJFo</a>"},{"pid":"35a89eddd141f097755babe61238a1b0af666738","tid":1204343,"uid":907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:56:28.000Z","msg":"靜坐人海，你我非不怕，會畏懼這樣下去怎辦。<br />\n<br />\n但是人生，到了這一晚，更怕未表達內心呼喊。"}]}